/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢為左保住HKG聲譽 <br />\n隻身去南河迎戰MK 但遭遇埋伏 幾百名MK一早降住把刀係條頸到等佢 <br />\n有人見到佢屎忽窿毛冇甩過一條 怯都冇怯到 <br />\n舉高把聖槍 大喊天道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n南河上天突然烏雲變色 雷電交加 仲落起一場腥風血雨 <br />\n班花生友突然被一道閃光 一秒 兩秒 三秒 就昏暈左鳥   <br />\n第二日 <br />\n南河出現左幾百條MK 訓哂係到似是比人炮轟過黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但見唔到大牌既蹤影 <br />\n有傳聞話 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢斬完MK出哂成身汗 單手游出左去南戴河消暑 <br />\n又有人話佢唔是普通人 而是天神 完成使命 被天庭號召返佢上天 <br />\n但係 係佢女朋友口中所得 <br />\n佢已經得到所有 <br />\n挑戰完鳥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c1cb379f927daa5f6f31cc96be42f180e3a05ca","tid":247044,"uid":15195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T13:56:47.000Z","msg":"點解可以咁lag"},{"pid":"8976e7e67beedc9adffae22f289b6b0d60fe696b","tid":247044,"uid":87154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T16:02:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當年大牌拎住把聖槍 係南河奔馳 <br />\n幾十名MK都封唔住佢 <br />\n眼望住佢任由屠殺 <br />\n揮下槍 一堆吃哂泥 放篤屁 又一堆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n班MK腳都震埋 企定定係到投哂降<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有人話全盛時期既佢 連SER都劈得爆<br />\n <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢為左保住HKG聲譽 <br />\n隻身去南河迎戰MK 但遭遇埋伏 幾百名MK一早降住把刀係條頸到等佢 <br />\n有人見到佢屎忽窿毛冇甩過一條 怯都冇怯到 <br />\n舉高把聖槍 大喊天道<img src=\