r />\n舉高把聖槍 大喊天道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n南河上天突然烏雲變色 雷電交加 仲落起一場腥風血雨 <br />\n班花生友突然被一道閃光 一秒 兩秒 三秒 就昏暈左鳥   <br />\n第二日 <br />\n南河出現左幾百條MK 訓哂係到似是比人炮轟過黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但見唔到大牌既蹤影 <br />\n有傳聞話 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢斬完MK出哂成身汗 單手游出左去南戴河消暑 <br />\n又有人話佢唔是普通人 而是天神 完成使命 被天庭號召返佢上天 <br />\n但係 係佢女朋友口中所得 <br />\n佢已經得到所有 <br />\n挑戰完鳥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大牌神<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你當年為左保住hkg聲譽 同戰友戰到力竭<br />\n當時我在場望住你118lv-》113<br />\n仲唔肯放棄 背負起所有戰友既力量<br />\n握緊手中聖槍 單槍匹馬勇闖南河<br />\n<br />\n之後所發生既事 我仲歷歷在望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你是咪患有大牌相思症<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然我都有呢個病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但不得不說大牌當年單槍赴會勇戰百個mk巔峰之戰<br />\n大戰後冇再到佢 聽聞為左女朋友 隱居田園過返平淡生活 <br />\n聖槍終封印南河底<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b7b87361551501acee5ef237623c4f91abad652","tid":247044,"uid":15195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T01:51:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解可以咁lag</blockquote><br />\n關下d效果 應該會好小小</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> hkbn關唔關事 見好多人玩 我好想玩 但有延遲 開書店都開左成分鐘 你地有冇呢啲問題"},{"pid":"0b064e40079841ba51f5cd526580eabf3a09c441","tid":247044,"uid":86175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T03:00:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"